<h2>Animations</h2>
<p>Animations (using the css <code>animate</code> property) allow for greater flexibility and control in comparison to simple transitions. Animations allow for the coordination of multiple transitions over time (through keyframes), repetition,and the ability to declare the direction of playback (forward, reversed, and alternate/boomerang).</p>

